     C                   MOVE      ICBS          LFICBS                                       232348
                                                                                              232348
      ** Calculation methods are:                                                             232348
                                                                                              232348
     C                   SELECT                                                               232348
                                                                                              232348
      ** 1 Actual/365, 4 365/365 (excluding 29/02)                                            232348
                                                                                              232348
     C                   WHEN      ICBS = 1 OR                                                232348
